title: "nanoGPT-Seis: the full LLM pretraining lifecycle on earthquake text"
abstract: >-
  A from-scratch, end-to-end small-LLM pretraining pipeline on earthquake /
  seismology text — crawl, clean, tokenize, a GQA+RoPE decoder, DDP training,
  and inference — built to make every stage legible.
